        <p><!--
The primary source for this edition is #Kolte_1972 (K). Shrimali (Shri) differs in some points, possibly being a reprint of Kolte's edition in VSMA (1971). I only refer to Shri where that edition differs from K. Corrections from #Shastri_1995 are referred to as S.
--><!--
I should note that the entire plate is extremely neatly written and contains much fewer errors than most Vākāṭaka plates.
